WEBVTT

00:08.241 --> 00:10.710
 Hey, Mikey, how are you doing?
 How was your weekend?

00:10.744 --> 00:12.746
  Can I borrow $300?

00:12.779 --> 00:15.448
 Fine, great, and not a chance.

00:15.482 --> 00:17.650
 Mikey, do you still have
 those savings bonds?

00:17.684 --> 00:20.120
Okay, Zack, what gives?

00:20.153 --> 00:22.255
 It was all my father's fault.

00:22.288 --> 00:25.091
  He told me not to fool around
  with his new video camera.

00:25.125 --> 00:27.427
   -What happened?
   -I fooled around with it.

00:27.460 --> 00:29.596
   You see, I was on my roof

00:29.629 --> 00:33.500
  taking pictures of the
  Zeffirelli twins doing
  aerobics in their backyard.

00:33.533 --> 00:36.436
 Zach, they live two blocks
 from your house.

00:36.469 --> 00:39.372
It's amazing what they've
done with zoom lenses.

00:39.406 --> 00:42.776
   I started to slip.
   It was either
   me or the camera.

00:42.809 --> 00:44.878
   I think you made
   the wrong choice.

00:44.911 --> 00:46.346
   Come on!

